queries.question: Rank customers by their total payments
queries.query: SELECT customer_id, SUM(amount) as total, RANK() OVER (ORDER BY SUM(amount) DESC) as rnk FROM payment GROUP BY customer_id;

queries.question: Calculate the running total of payments for each customer
queries.query: SELECT customer_id, payment_date, amount, SUM(amount) OVER (PARTITION BY customer_id ORDER BY payment_date) as running_total FROM payment;

queries.question: Compare each film's replacement cost with the average replacement cost of its rating category
queries.query: SELECT title, rating, replacement_cost, AVG(replacement_cost) OVER (PARTITION BY rating) as avg_cost_for_rating FROM film;

queries.question: Find the lag difference in payment amounts for each customer
queries.query: SELECT customer_id, payment_date, amount, amount - LAG(amount) OVER (PARTITION BY customer_id ORDER BY payment_date) as diff FROM payment;
